# Phase Completion: Commit and Push

After completing each phase of the Easy Approval architecture plan:

1. Stage all changes: `git add -A`
2. Commit with a descriptive message including phase number and what was done
3. Push to origin: `git push origin main`

GitHub credentials are configured in the project. Do not commit `.env.local` or any file containing tokens.
